    "\\n",
    "Queries Fitbit parquet tables directly from R2 using DuckDB.\\n",
    "\\n",
    "Tables: \`fitbit_calories\`, \`fitbit_steps\`, \`fitbit_sleep\`, \`fitbit_exercise\`"
